column17:
The following post uses a distract tactic by discussing an irrelevant topic:

@PrimeVideo @SpongeBob Save 1899. It deserves its full three seasons. Outstanding show. #Save1899

This post is distracting from the main topic of environmental issues by discussing the renewal of a TV show, 1899. It shifts the focus away from environmental concerns to a television show, making it a distract tactic.

column28:
The post that uses a Dismiss tactic is: 

@netflix Shame you cancel everything else https://t.co/C5iGWqkOjs

This post dismisses the importance of the topic (renewing the show 1899) by suggesting that Netflix cancels everything else, implying that the cancellation of this show is not a big deal compared to other shows being canceled.
